c: 24
v: 3
t: "alzaani la yardaa 'iilaa bnkah zaniatan 'aw mushrikatan la tuqirr bhrmt alzna, walzaaniat la trda 'iilaa bnkah zan 'aw mushrik la yuqirr bhrmt alzna، 'amaa alefyfwn walefyfat fa'iinahum la yrdwn bdhlk, whurrim dhlk alnikah ealaa almwmnyn. whdha dalil sarih ealaa tahrim nkah alzaaniat hataa ttwb, wkdhlk tahrim 'inkah alzaani hataa ytwb"